sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant EmailService
    participant SMSService
    participant Support

    User->>System: Request Account Recovery
    System->>User: Send recovery options (email/SMS)
    User->>EmailService: Request recovery email
    EmailService-->>User: Send recovery link
    User->>System: Click recovery link
    System->>User: Verify identity (security questions)
    User->>System: Provide answers
    System->>User: Identity verified

    User->>System: Request Number Change
    System->>User: Send verification code via SMS
    User->>SMSService: Request verification code
    SMSService-->>User: Send verification code
    User->>System: Enter verification code
    System->>User: Verify code
    User->>System: Confirm new number
    System->>User: Update number and notify
    User->>Support: Report device loss
    Support-->>User: Provide recovery steps